gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="位于挪威安岛航天港的伊萨尔航空航天发射台。资料来源：伊萨尔航空航天公司" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i9YeqKh5Xlho/v1/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt;安岛航天港的伊萨尔航空航天发射台。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;资料来源：伊萨尔航空航天公司&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;人们迟来地认识到，与欧洲国防、安全、贸易和技术的其他方面一样，实现太空主权正在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/EIcvs0JB4z2u4b1QZBkIb66z8yNUZ4dTavifcWbi-o6uJWlMy86Q3-K1nDWvFgYDR4xIpjlpj0DOWYeTGocBte8V94QQc1gG0YoVnUz3B9s-gD-CCc0VLhzQoY6vaUWrbhw7Zq1_B6osOlDrykRV9ROPcQJyIxZ2QVH8-GJIaImF_0bZ_9iLXkz7owhqlhMN1W7xtpERZvXIsK4WDHTE-78P5acEItNQqmgA4Vczats2cAwOvL56YLvg5IhWlj3OFouQifRY616EHKJRtGa42Hh3gdAuLLMcbUBUtFePObTybbwswEXJILvsjdenKczsL2DXhCgribOLflPGIEVrCuwfyzszc5maq3CDLx_yoekCuOwyPWCZpcCuC9jifVT3WDSfucp0cnEZl_dGABJf-uj1pvo_t-QxfsPtx3uqVntNykstPU35uFSu1YXmgyMeXRiw6yNLksdg8yWDV8pyM_RbCHBMDuFnA-lw_khdK43PQTHAYS-OxmsAsMDLs5AIveAcvpi4Mr_U15NOVj-ikC4UJIjXf7jvM5ve_7aO/wqoYpxYk7UM24PgMsjFkicEAZgTiqzuk/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="火箭短缺使欧洲在太空战争中毫无防御能力"&gt;成为一项战略要务&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;没有什么比用于观测、通信和地理定位的卫星以及&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/ApJd5sZm8CPTvdHW5Ql2o_S2R1vgRVxsudnenVlIQ89DwPX7OSLn9U74MC8t5tfds5zWDlR-5Ne2gFaKR-UL-GMnXwkqI0Zafa28h-pmD9AJC-KLHF3eS-G89uRjepiPpPMPLhFLqxFYP3DyhfHSaZXWPE31EN76Af8mjmOhWunWWlrrP5f9kTPmZgOSVKIRAm-VpPWTWHqd22B1MbKRaTI4nQpNZooy2k4SMNssNucMXXu0L3xDjKhOoFrDFUFty-0w6gHHmKwmS31Vl51SbFCd00hPEhmUeTGqADcs9_HUxKwBvpxbF3Xt2DAN8SylOjmDDqD7Cc2QuFdNMCo0otPpHn_VWyD_egPOBkH1yqiSHCB2ZjOG97RPS4_7L_iJbHakWd6lu6LCf7lMUyrZnbFPKYKLzUdq0sw5ojRgsJyQOMJeVYMRN9USi